{
  "video_id": "pVeq-0dIqpk",
  "title": "How to build (and rebuild) trust | Frances Frei",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13889.0,
      "end_time": 17906.0,
      "text": "I want to talk to you about how to build and rebuild trust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17930.0,
      "end_time": 20698.0,
      "text": "because it's my belief that trust"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20723.0,
      "end_time": 24649.0,
      "text": "is the foundation for everything we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24673.0,
      "end_time": 29101.0,
      "text": "and that if we can learn to trust one another more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29126.0,
      "end_time": 32220.0,
      "text": "we can have unprecedented human progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 35277.0,
      "end_time": 37990.0,
      "text": "But what if trust is broken?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 38531.0,
      "end_time": 43634.0,
      "text": "What if your CEO is caught on video, disparaging an employee?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 45646.0,
      "end_time": 52392.0,
      "text": "What if your employees experience a culture of bias, exclusion and worse?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 53742.0,
      "end_time": 55924.0,
      "text": "What if there's a data breach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 55948.0,
      "end_time": 61194.0,
      "text": "and it feels an awful lot like a cover-up than seriously addressing it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 62808.0,
      "end_time": 64681.0,
      "text": "And most tragically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 64705.0,
      "end_time": 69459.0,
      "text": "what if a technological fail leads to the loss of human life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 71900.0,
      "end_time": 73312.0,
      "text": "If I was giving this talk six months ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 73336.0,
      "end_time": 75844.0,
      "text": "I would have been wearing an Uber T-shirt."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 78509.0,
      "end_time": 80747.0,
      "text": "I'm a Harvard Business School professor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 80771.0,
      "end_time": 85495.0,
      "text": "but I was super attracted to going to an organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 85519.0,
      "end_time": 90818.0,
      "text": "that was metaphorically and perhaps quite literally on fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 92570.0,
      "end_time": 95190.0,
      "text": "I had read everything that was written in the newspaper,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 95214.0,
      "end_time": 99271.0,
      "text": "and that was precisely what drew me to the organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 99295.0,
      "end_time": 102866.0,
      "text": "This was an organization that had lost trust"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 102890.0,
      "end_time": 106177.0,
      "text": "with every constituent that mattered."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 107460.0,
      "end_time": 110149.0,
      "text": "But there's a word about me that I should share."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 110174.0,
      "end_time": 112642.0,
      "text": "My favorite trait is redemption."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 114640.0,
      "end_time": 118975.0,
      "text": "I believe that there is a better version of us around every corner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 118999.0,
      "end_time": 120838.0,
      "text": "and I have seen firsthand"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 120862.0,
      "end_time": 123539.0,
      "text": "how organizations and communities"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 123564.0,
      "end_time": 126755.0,
      "text": "and individuals change at breathtaking speed."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 128467.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132697.0,
      "text": "I went to Uber with the hope of a turn around there"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 132721.0,
      "end_time": 135303.0,
      "text": "could give license to the rest of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 135327.0,
      "end_time": 138986.0,
      "text": "who might have narrower versions of their challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 141660.0,
      "end_time": 144776.0,
      "text": "But when I got to Uber, I made a really big mistake."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 146343.0,
      "end_time": 151619.0,
      "text": "I publicly committed to wearing an Uber T-shirt every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 151644.0,
      "end_time": 154778.0,
      "text": "until every other employee was wearing an Uber T-shirt."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 156179.0,
      "end_time": 159380.0,
      "text": "I had clearly not thought that through."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 159620.0,
      "end_time": 160710.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 160734.0,
      "end_time": 165143.0,
      "text": "It was 250 days of wearing an Uber T-shirt."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 166119.0,
      "end_time": 170498.0,
      "text": "Now I am liberated from that commitment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 170522.0,
      "end_time": 172721.0,
      "text": "as I am back at HBS,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 172745.0,
      "end_time": 176930.0,
      "text": "and what I'd like to do is share with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 176954.0,
      "end_time": 181550.0,
      "text": "how far I have taken that liberty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 181790.0,
      "end_time": 184174.0,
      "text": "which, it's baby steps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 184198.0,
      "end_time": 185428.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 185452.0,
      "end_time": 187459.0,
      "text": "but I would just say I'm on my way."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 187483.0,
      "end_time": 189199.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 189223.0,
      "end_time": 192787.0,
      "text": "Now, trust, if we're going to rebuild it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 192811.0,
      "end_time": 195427.0,
      "text": "we have to understand its component parts."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 195890.0,
      "end_time": 199748.0,
      "text": "The component parts of trust are super well understood."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 199772.0,
      "end_time": 202462.0,
      "text": "There's three things about trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 204349.0,
      "end_time": 208733.0,
      "text": "If you sense that I am being authentic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 208757.0,
      "end_time": 210999.0,
      "text": "you are much more likely to trust me."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 212147.0,
      "end_time": 217695.0,
      "text": "If you sense that I have real rigor in my logic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 217719.0,
      "end_time": 219861.0,
      "text": "you are far more likely to trust me."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 220528.0,
      "end_time": 225441.0,
      "text": "And if you believe that my empathy is directed towards you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 225465.0,
      "end_time": 227692.0,
      "text": "you are far more likely to trust me."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 228303.0,
      "end_time": 231103.0,
      "text": "When all three of these things are working,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 231128.0,
      "end_time": 233247.0,
      "text": "we have great trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 234165.0,
      "end_time": 237539.0,
      "text": "But if any one of these three gets shaky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 237563.0,
      "end_time": 241188.0,
      "text": "if any one of these three wobbles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 241212.0,
      "end_time": 242648.0,
      "text": "trust is threatened."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 244291.0,
      "end_time": 246470.0,
      "text": "Now here's what I'd like to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 246710.0,
      "end_time": 251228.0,
      "text": "I want each of us to be able to engender more trust tomorrow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 251252.0,
      "end_time": 253744.0,
      "text": "literally tomorrow, than we do today."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 255339.0,
      "end_time": 261158.0,
      "text": "And the way to do that is to understand where trust wobbles for ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 261182.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263864.0,
      "text": "and have a ready-made prescription to overcome it."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 264460.0,
      "end_time": 266650.0,
      "text": "So that's what I would like to do together."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 268390.0,
      "end_time": 271936.0,
      "text": "Would you give me some sense of whether or not you're here voluntarily?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 271960.0,
      "end_time": 273460.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 273710.0,
      "end_time": 275435.0,
      "text": "Yeah. OK. Alright. Awesome."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 275459.0,
      "end_time": 276969.0,
      "text": "OK. So --"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 276993.0,
      "end_time": 278332.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 278357.0,
      "end_time": 280123.0,
      "text": "it's just super helpful feedback."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 280147.0,
      "end_time": 282433.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 282457.0,
      "end_time": 287512.0,
      "text": "So the most common wobble is empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 289610.0,
      "end_time": 290385.0,
      "text": "The most common wobble"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 290410.0,
      "end_time": 295392.0,
      "text": "is that people just don't believe that we're mostly in it for them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 295416.0,
      "end_time": 298588.0,
      "text": "and they believe that we're too self-distracted."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 299423.0,
      "end_time": 300981.0,
      "text": "And it's no wonder."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 301500.0,
      "end_time": 304613.0,
      "text": "We are all so busy with so many demands on our time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 304637.0,
      "end_time": 308334.0,
      "text": "it's easy to crowd out the time and space"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 308358.0,
      "end_time": 310859.0,
      "text": "that empathy requires."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 310883.0,
      "end_time": 313818.0,
      "text": "For Dylan to be Dylan, that takes real time."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 315276.0,
      "end_time": 320442.0,
      "text": "And for us, if we have too much to do, we may not have that time."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 320466.0,
      "end_time": 322965.0,
      "text": "But that puts us into a vicious cycle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 322989.0,
      "end_time": 325734.0,
      "text": "because without revealing empathy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 325759.0,
      "end_time": 327974.0,
      "text": "it makes everything harder."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 327998.0,
      "end_time": 331664.0,
      "text": "Without the benefit of the doubt of trust, it makes everything harder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 331689.0,
      "end_time": 335498.0,
      "text": "and then we have less and less time for empathy, and so it goes."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 336232.0,
      "end_time": 337720.0,
      "text": "So here's the prescription:"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 339660.0,
      "end_time": 346351.0,
      "text": "identify where, when and to whom"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 346375.0,
      "end_time": 349250.0,
      "text": "you are likely to offer your distraction."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 351161.0,
      "end_time": 354249.0,
      "text": "That should trace pretty perfectly"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 354273.0,
      "end_time": 359709.0,
      "text": "to when, where and to whom you are likely to withhold your empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 361123.0,
      "end_time": 363724.0,
      "text": "And if in those instances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 363748.0,
      "end_time": 369993.0,
      "text": "we can come up with a trigger that gets us to look up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 370170.0,
      "end_time": 373140.0,
      "text": "look at the people right in front of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 373164.0,
      "end_time": 374973.0,
      "text": "listen to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 374997.0,
      "end_time": 379137.0,
      "text": "deeply immerse ourselves in their perspectives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 379161.0,
      "end_time": 384114.0,
      "text": "then we have a chance of having a sturdy leg of empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 384811.0,
      "end_time": 386635.0,
      "text": "And if you do nothing else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 387902.0,
      "end_time": 391164.0,
      "text": "please put away your cell phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 391787.0,
      "end_time": 396775.0,
      "text": "It is the largest distraction magnet yet to be made,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 396800.0,
      "end_time": 402305.0,
      "text": "and it is super difficult to create empathy and trust in its presence."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 404241.0,
      "end_time": 406251.0,
      "text": "That takes care of the empathy wobblers."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 408140.0,
      "end_time": 411330.0,
      "text": "Logic wobbles can come in two forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 412189.0,
      "end_time": 415223.0,
      "text": "It's either the quality of your logic"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 416752.0,
      "end_time": 419969.0,
      "text": "or it's your ability to communicate the logic."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 420777.0,
      "end_time": 424483.0,
      "text": "Now if the quality of your logic is at risk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 424507.0,
      "end_time": 426135.0,
      "text": "I can't really help you with that."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 426159.0,
      "end_time": 427498.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 427522.0,
      "end_time": 429167.0,
      "text": "It's like, not in this much time."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 429191.0,
      "end_time": 432654.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 432678.0,
      "end_time": 437758.0,
      "text": "But fortunately, it's often the case that our logic is sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 437782.0,
      "end_time": 443270.0,
      "text": "but it's our ability to communicate the logic that is in jeopardy."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 443295.0,
      "end_time": 446873.0,
      "text": "Super fortunately, there's a very easy fix to this."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 447673.0,
      "end_time": 453643.0,
      "text": "If we consider that there are two ways to communicate in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 453667.0,
      "end_time": 456809.0,
      "text": "and Harvard Business School professors are known for two-by-twos --"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 456834.0,
      "end_time": 459302.0,
      "text": "nonsense, it's the triangle that rocks."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 459326.0,
      "end_time": 461482.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 462837.0,
      "end_time": 467120.0,
      "text": "If we consider that there are two ways to communicate in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 467360.0,
      "end_time": 471650.0,
      "text": "and the first one is when you take us on a journey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 471674.0,
      "end_time": 476657.0,
      "text": "a magnificent journey that has twists and turns"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 476681.0,
      "end_time": 479813.0,
      "text": "and mystery and drama,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 479837.0,
      "end_time": 482324.0,
      "text": "until you ultimately get to the point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 483536.0,
      "end_time": 486612.0,
      "text": "and some of the best communicators in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 486636.0,
      "end_time": 488667.0,
      "text": "communicate just like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 489432.0,
      "end_time": 491964.0,
      "text": "But if you have a logic wobble,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 491988.0,
      "end_time": 494170.0,
      "text": "this can be super dangerous."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 495310.0,
      "end_time": 498136.0,
      "text": "So instead, I implore you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 499856.0,
      "end_time": 505790.0,
      "text": "start with your point in a crisp half-sentence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 505103.0,
      "end_time": 508790.0,
      "text": "and then give your supporting evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 509777.0,
      "end_time": 512193.0,
      "text": "This means that people will be able to get access"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 512217.0,
      "end_time": 514410.0,
      "text": "to our awesome ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 514433.99999999994,
      "end_time": 516769.99999999994,
      "text": "and just as importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 517585.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520227.00000000006,
      "text": "if you get cut off before you're done ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 521894.0,
      "end_time": 523322.0,
      "text": "ladies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 523346.0,
      "end_time": 525941.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 525965.0,
      "end_time": 532770.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 532794.0,
      "end_time": 536217.0,
      "text": "If you get cut off before you're done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 536241.0,
      "end_time": 538160.0,
      "text": "you still get credit for the idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 538184.0,
      "end_time": 541741.0,
      "text": "as opposed to someone else coming in and snatching it from you."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 541765.0,
      "end_time": 548335.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 548359.0,
      "end_time": 549693.0,
      "text": "You just gave me goosebumps."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 549717.0,
      "end_time": 551193.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 551920.0,
      "end_time": 556269.0,
      "text": "The third wobble is authenticity, and I find it to be the most vexing."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 557730.0,
      "end_time": 561104.0,
      "text": "We as a human species can sniff out in a moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 561128.0,
      "end_time": 563116.0,
      "text": "literally in a moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 563140.0,
      "end_time": 566164.0,
      "text": "whether or not someone is being their authentic true self."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 567705.0,
      "end_time": 569990.0,
      "text": "So in many ways, the prescription is clear."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 570948.0,
      "end_time": 574174.0,
      "text": "You don't want to have an authenticity wobble? Be you."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 575675.0,
      "end_time": 576881.0,
      "text": "Great."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 578255.0,
      "end_time": 580525.0,
      "text": "And that is super easy to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 580549.0,
      "end_time": 583890.0,
      "text": "when you're around people who are like you."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 585817.0,
      "end_time": 589317.0,
      "text": "But if you represent any sort of difference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 590659.0,
      "end_time": 595206.0,
      "text": "the prescription to \"be you\" can be super challenging."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 597905.0,
      "end_time": 601996.0,
      "text": "I have been tempted at every step of my career,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 602200.0,
      "end_time": 605293.0,
      "text": "tempted personally and tempted by coaching of others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 605317.0,
      "end_time": 607563.0,
      "text": "to mute who I am in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 608688.0,
      "end_time": 611738.0,
      "text": "I'm a woman of super strong opinions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 611762.0,
      "end_time": 614396.0,
      "text": "with really deep convictions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 614421.0,
      "end_time": 616370.0,
      "text": "direct speech."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 616602.0,
      "end_time": 619236.0,
      "text": "I have a magnificent wife,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 619260.0,
      "end_time": 622529.0,
      "text": "and together, we have such crazy ambition."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 623950.0,
      "end_time": 625807.0,
      "text": "I prefer men's clothes"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 626743.0,
      "end_time": 628267.0,
      "text": "and comfortable shoes."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 629450.0,
      "end_time": 630457.0,
      "text": "Thank you, Allbirds."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 630481.0,
      "end_time": 633617.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 633642.0,
      "end_time": 637102.0,
      "text": "In some contexts, this makes me different."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 638229.0,
      "end_time": 640321.0,
      "text": "I hope that each person here"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 640345.0,
      "end_time": 644121.0,
      "text": "has the beautiful luxury of representing difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 644145.0,
      "end_time": 645997.0,
      "text": "in some context in your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 647295.0,
      "end_time": 649430.0,
      "text": "But with that privilege"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 650154.0,
      "end_time": 655911.0,
      "text": "comes a very sincere temptation to hold back who we are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 655935.0,
      "end_time": 658301.0,
      "text": "and if we hold back who we are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 658326.0,
      "end_time": 660395.0,
      "text": "we're less likely to be trusted."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 660419.0,
      "end_time": 662332.0,
      "text": "And if we're less likely to be trusted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 662356.0,
      "end_time": 665109.0,
      "text": "we're less likely to be given stretch assignments."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 665133.0,
      "end_time": 668562.0,
      "text": "And without those stretch assignments, we're less likely to get promoted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 668586.0,
      "end_time": 672134.0,
      "text": "and so on and so on until we are super depressed"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 672158.0,
      "end_time": 675650.0,
      "text": "by the demographic tendencies of our senior leadership."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 675518.0,
      "end_time": 676966.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 676990.0,
      "end_time": 683746.0,
      "text": "And it all comes back to our being our authentic selves."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 683770.0,
      "end_time": 685989.0,
      "text": "So here's my advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 686130.0,
      "end_time": 688712.0,
      "text": "Wear whatever makes you feel fabulous."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 690434.0,
      "end_time": 694725.0,
      "text": "Pay less attention to what you think people want to hear from you"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 694749.0,
      "end_time": 699712.0,
      "text": "and far more attention to what your authentic, awesome self needs to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 701127.0,
      "end_time": 702990.0,
      "text": "And to the leaders in the room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 704379.0,
      "end_time": 706555.0,
      "text": "it is your obligation"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 706579.0,
      "end_time": 711745.0,
      "text": "to set the conditions that not only make it safe for us to be authentic"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 711769.0,
      "end_time": 713182.0,
      "text": "but make it welcome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 714713.0,
      "end_time": 716356.0,
      "text": "make it celebrated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 716975.0,
      "end_time": 720516.0,
      "text": "cherish it for exactly what it is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 720540.0,
      "end_time": 723901.0,
      "text": "which is the key for us achieving greater excellence"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 723926.0,
      "end_time": 726265.0,
      "text": "than we have ever known is possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 728416.0,
      "end_time": 731716.0,
      "text": "So let's go back to Uber. What happened at Uber?"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 731740.0,
      "end_time": 735918.0,
      "text": "When I got there, Uber was wobbling all over the place."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 736913.0,
      "end_time": 741560.0,
      "text": "Empathy, logic, authenticity were all wobbling like crazy."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 742528.0,
      "end_time": 748385.0,
      "text": "But we were able to find super effective, super quick fixes for two of the wobbles."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 749636.0,
      "end_time": 752199.0,
      "text": "I'll give you an illustration of empathy."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 752223.0,
      "end_time": 753597.0,
      "text": "In the meetings at Uber,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 753621.0,
      "end_time": 757605.0,
      "text": "it was not uncommon for people to be texting one another ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 758965.0,
      "end_time": 760156.0,
      "text": "about the meeting."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 760180.0,
      "end_time": 765931.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 765956.0,
      "end_time": 768226.0,
      "text": "I had never seen anything like it."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 768250.0,
      "end_time": 769678.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 770305.0,
      "end_time": 771742.0,
      "text": "It may have done many things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 771767.0,
      "end_time": 775241.0,
      "text": "but it did not create a safe, empathetic environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 775612.0,
      "end_time": 778160.0,
      "text": "The solution though, super clear:"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 778400.0,
      "end_time": 779770.0,
      "text": "technology, off and away."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 780886.0,
      "end_time": 783568.0,
      "text": "And that forced people to look up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 783592.0,
      "end_time": 786244.0,
      "text": "to look at the people in front of them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 786268.0,
      "end_time": 787666.0,
      "text": "to listen to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 787690.0,
      "end_time": 789769.0,
      "text": "to immerse themselves in their perspectives"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 789793.0,
      "end_time": 793213.0,
      "text": "and to collaborate in unprecedented ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 795128.0,
      "end_time": 798749.0,
      "text": "Logic was equally wobbly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 798773.0,
      "end_time": 801670.0,
      "text": "and this was because the hypergrowth of the organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 801694.0,
      "end_time": 804361.0,
      "text": "meant that people, managers were getting promoted"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 804385.0,
      "end_time": 806523.0,
      "text": "again and again and again."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 807281.0,
      "end_time": 810988.0,
      "text": "Soon, they were put in positions that they had no business being in."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 811818.0,
      "end_time": 814124.0,
      "text": "Their positions outstripped their capability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 814148.0,
      "end_time": 815635.0,
      "text": "and it was not their fault."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 816600.0,
      "end_time": 821330.0,
      "text": "The solution: a massive influx of executive education"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 821354.0,
      "end_time": 825120.0,
      "text": "that focused specifically on logic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 825360.0,
      "end_time": 827227.0,
      "text": "on strategy and leadership."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 828119.0,
      "end_time": 831563.0,
      "text": "It gave people the rigor of the quality of their logic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 831587.0,
      "end_time": 836747.0,
      "text": "and it turned a whole lot of triangles, right-side up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 836771.0,
      "end_time": 840000.0,
      "text": "so people were able to communicate effectively with one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 841554.0,
      "end_time": 846930.0,
      "text": "The last one, authenticity, I'll say it's still mighty wobbly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 847173.0,
      "end_time": 849642.0,
      "text": "but honestly, that doesn't make Uber very different"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 849666.0,
      "end_time": 853196.0,
      "text": "from all of the other companies I've seen in Silicon Valley and beyond."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 855194.0,
      "end_time": 859726.0,
      "text": "It is still much easier to coach people to fit in."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 860627.0,
      "end_time": 863705.0,
      "text": "It is still much easier to reward people"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 863730.0,
      "end_time": 867117.0,
      "text": "when they say something that you were going to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 867141.0,
      "end_time": 869673.0,
      "text": "as opposed to rewarding people when they say something"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 869697.0,
      "end_time": 872426.0,
      "text": "entirely different than what you were going to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 874157.0,
      "end_time": 876676.0,
      "text": "But when we figure out this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 876700.0,
      "end_time": 880370.0,
      "text": "when we figure out how to celebrate difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 880394.0,
      "end_time": 883965.0,
      "text": "and how to let people bring the best version of themselves forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 883989.0,
      "end_time": 888430.0,
      "text": "well holy cow, is that the world I want my sons to grow up in."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 889280.0,
      "end_time": 891295.0,
      "text": "And with the collection of people here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 891320.0,
      "end_time": 894449.0,
      "text": "it would be a privilege to lock arms with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 894473.0,
      "end_time": 898300.0,
      "text": "and go ahead and rebuild trust in every corner of the globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 898838.0,
      "end_time": 899988.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 900130.0,
      "end_time": 904611.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}